---
title: Smokey Eggplant Salad & Mint Couscous  with Slivered Almonds & Garlic Yoghurt Dressing
description: Tonight’s salad is hearty and flavourful, with fluffy couscous, roasted eggplant and mint all tossed together. We’ll mix up a garlicky yoghurt dressing as well for extra pizzazz - drizzle it all over for an extra touch of creamy tartness, and sprinkle over some almonds for that much-needed crunch!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

